<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="Fronteers Belgium organises casual front-end development meetups across Flanders. Join us to learn, share, and connect with fellow front-end developers.">
    <title>Fronteers meetups Belgium</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{'/assets/theme.css' | url }}" />
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>🤩</text></svg>">

  </head>
  <body>
    <header role="banner">
      <h1>
        <span class="sr-only">Fronteers</span>
        {% icon "custom:logo", class="logo"  %}
        <span>meetups Belgium</span>
      </h1>
      <nav aria-labelledby="social-media-label" class="social-media">
        <span id="social-media-label"><b>Find us on:</b></span>
        <ul class="social-media__list">
          <li class="social-media__item">
            <a class="social-media__link" 
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/fronteers-belgium/"
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer" >
              LinkedIn</a>
          </li>
          <li class="social-media__item">
            <a class="social-media__link" 
              href="https://www.meetup.com/fronteers-be/"
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer" >
            Meetup</a>
          </li>
          <li class="social-media__item">
            <a class="social-media__link"
            href="https://tally.so/r/Gxd72e" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer">Newsletter
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <main role="main">
      <section class="introduction">
        <p>
          <strong>
           We are a community for people with an interest in front-end development and we host casual meetups in Flanders, Belgium.
          </strong>
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="events">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Join an upcoming event</h2>
          <ul class="event__list">
            {# <li class="event__list-item">
              <span>
                {% icon "custom:calendar" %}
              </span>
              <a class="event__link" href="https://www.meetup.com/fronteers-be/events/313061874/" target="_blank">
                <time datetime="2024-03-07T18:00">Thu 12 Mar</time> Craftzing - Ghent
              </a>
            </li> #}
            <li class="event__list-item">
              <span>
                {% icon "custom:calendar" %}
              </span>
              <p class="event__placeholder">Currently planning our next meetup</p>
            </li>
            <li class="event__list-item">
              <span>
                {% icon "custom:microphone" %}
              </span>
              <a class="event__link" href="https://tally.so/r/waXWX3" target="_blank">
                Want to speak at a future meetup?
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="community-survey">
        <div>
        <p><strong>Do you have a minute to spare? We have a few questions for our community members.</strong><br><a target="_blank" href="https://tally.so/r/rjOy7M">You can find them here.</a></p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="atmosphere">
        <h2>Sniff up the atmosphere</h2>
        <div class="image__group">
          <img
            class="image portrait"
            src="/assets/images/fronteersbe-itp-2022-1.jpg" 
            alt="The still empty meetup space, with chairs set up to face the small stage and presenter screen. On the presenter screen a slide is visible introducting the Fronteers BE meetup." 
          />
          <img
            class="image landscape"
            src="/assets/images/fronteersbe-io-2024.png"
            alt="Emma facilitating a discussion around the ethical responsibilities of software developers."
          />
          <img
            class="image portrait"
            src="/assets/images/fronteersbe-io-2024-2.png"
            alt="Elian giving a talk about 'Going full stack with Astro'" 
          />
          <img
            class="image landscape"
            src="/assets/images/fronteersbe-craftzing-2026.png"
            alt="Claudia introducing the new Fronteers Belgium team!" 
          />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="support-us">
        <div class="card" id="eventspeakers">
          <h2>Join an event as speaker</h2>
          <p>
            Interested in talking about a front-end related subject? Or maybe something front-end enthusiasts can relate to?<br><br> We welcome people of all levels.
          </p>
          <a class="card__cto" 
            href="https://tally.so/r/waXWX3"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Leave your info</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card" id="eventhosts">
          <h2>Host a Fronteers event</h2>
          <p>
            Are you part of a tech company with front-end developers amongst 
            their ranks and interested in hosting an event?</p>
          <a class="card__cto" 
            href="https://tally.so/r/3yL4pm"
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Submit company</a>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="team">
        <h2>The team behind the events</h2>
        <ul class="organisers">
          <li class="organiser-profile">
            <img 
             class="image"
             src="/assets/images/claudia.jpg"
             {# widths: [200], #}
             alt="Headshot of Claudia R"
             />
            <h3>Claudia R</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/claudia_rndrs"
                  target="_blank" 
                  rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  LinkedIn</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li class="organiser-profile">
            <img 
             class="image"
             src="/assets/images/joeri.png"
             {# widths= [200], #}
             alt="Headshot of Joeri S"
             />
            <h3>Joeri S</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a href="https://be.linkedin.com/in/joeri-sebrechts-b20a752b"
                  target="_blank" 
                  rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  LinkedIn</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li class="organiser-profile">
            <img 
             class="image"
             src="/assets/images/rune.png"
             {# widths: [200], #}
             alt="Headshot of Rune D"
             />
            <h3>Rune D</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a href="https://be.linkedin.com/in/runedevuyst"
                  target="_blank" 
                  rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  LinkedIn</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li class="organiser-profile">
            <img 
             class="image"
             src="/assets/images/vu.png"
             {# widths: [200], #}
             alt="Headshot of Vuong (Vu) H"
             />
            <h3>Vu H</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a href="https://be.linkedin.com/in/vuong-ha-8aa46528"
                  target="_blank" 
                  rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  LinkedIn</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li class="organiser-profile">
            <img 
             class="image"
             src="/assets/images/yannick.png"
             {# widths: [200], #}
             alt="Headshot of Yannick H"
             />
            <h3>Yannick H</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a href="https://be.linkedin.com/in/yannickhoubrix"
                  target="_blank" 
                  rel="noopener noreferrer">
                  LinkedIn</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li class="organiser-profile">
            <picture class="image image__placeholder">
              <span>🤩</span>
            </picture>
            <h3>You?</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <p>We are looking for more team members in Antwerp, Limburg and Vlaams-Brabant to help us organise events. <strong>Contact Claudia for info</strong>.</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Any Questions?</h3>
        <p><a href="mailto:belgie@fronteers.nl">Reach out to
          us</a>
          for anything event-related.</p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <p>Want to receive event updates in your mailbox?
        <a 
          href="https://tally.so/r/Gxd72e" 
          target="_blank" 
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Join our newsletter waitinglist.
        </a>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
